<item>
            <title>[LU-6156] sanity test 27D failure: llapi_layout_test failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6156</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;while running the sanity test suite, sanity test 27D failed with &quot;llapi_layout_test failed&quot;. Results are at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/37e63f92-9f0d-11e4-91b3-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/37e63f92-9f0d-11e4-91b3-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt; . &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tests 16 and 20 of the llapi_layout_tests failed with the same assertion:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;...
llapi_layout_test: llapi_layout_test.c:708: test16: assertion &apos;fcount == dcount&apos; failed: 6 != 1152921504606846979
 test 16: Default stripe attributes are applied as expected . fail (exit status 1)
...
llapi_layout_test: llapi_layout_test.c:887: test20: assertion &apos;fcount == dcount&apos; failed: 6 != 1152921504606846979
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All other llapi_layout_test passed. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>OpenSFS cluster with two MDSs with one MDT each, three OSSs with two OSTs each and three clients running lustre-master tag 2.6.92 build # 2812</environment>
